#

Pumpkin Spiced Bread Pudding

$12.5
420 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

dairyeggsgluten

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Tags:

dessertautumncomfort food

Description

A warm, comforting dessert featuring rich pumpkin spices and creamy custard-soaked bread, perfect for autumn evenings.

Ingredients

  • day-old brioche bread: 6 cups, cubed
  • pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • heavy cream: 2 cups
  • whole milk: 1 cup
  • granulated sugar: 1 cup
  • eggs: 4 large
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
  • ground cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • ground nutmeg: 1/2 teaspoon
  • ground ginger: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/4 teaspoon
  • butter: 2 tablespoons, melted
